{"type": "article", "id": 35446, "title": "这些工具，想让你在下厨时多一份乐趣｜这个设计了不起", "description": "每个周末，《好奇心日报》都会找个主题为你寻找精彩设计。", "date": "2016-12-10T01:08:20Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 7, "praise_count": 295, "image": "img/article/article_show/20161209221955Tur2pLfMj8O5PgCH.jpg", "contents": "<p>        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 27.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} </style>  </p><p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。</p><p class=\"\">烹饪就像是一门艺术：食材的搭配以及份量和温度的把控，无不在考验掌勺人的知识储备、技巧以及创造力。本周的推荐就是那些能让下厨变得省力又有趣的工具。</p><p>        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #323333} p.p2 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #323333; min-height: 25.0px} p.p3 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 18.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #323333; min-height: 25.0px} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} </style>  </p><h3>Drop Scale by Drop Kitchen Inc.</h3><p>面对菜谱上那些量化的指导，想在没有秤的情况下做好一道菜颇有难度。成立于爱尔兰的 Drop Kitchen 是一家专注于厨房智能化的公司，旗下的第一款产品就是名为 Drop 的智能电子秤。由于它需要和安装了配套 App 的设备一起使用，省去显示屏的它有着简约的外观，红色的秤盘搭配白色的圆形底座，小巧实用。除了称量和本身强大的菜谱库之外，如果你手头上没有所需的材料，它还会为你向你推荐替代品。美中不足的是，它目前仅支持 iOS 系统。这是它的<a href=\"https://www.getdrop.com/order\" rel=\"nofollow\">购买链接</a>，售价为 79.95 美元。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161209214547fAdEaqRv3IXl0N7t.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.522500\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161209214547tX8SrVNOb4pR5Ad2.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161209214529ulWdmpqebVI35Y4P.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562500\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161209214530XMe4iqGZmR1usAdn.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.794118\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Polygons by Rahul Agarwal</h3><p>        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #323333} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} </style>  </p><p>你或许没有想过，弯弯的量勺也可以扁平化。几个月前，<a href=\"http://www.qdaily.com/articles/33313.html\">我们曾经介绍过</a>这款来自印度的设计师 Rahul Agarwal 带来的造型非常亮眼的勺子——之所以用“张”做量词，是因为它在普通情况下就是一张用柔韧的热塑性橡胶制成的平板。这块红色的长方形板上的刻度和折痕隐约可见，可以在四种尺寸中切换。你还可以通过<a href=\"https://www.indiegogo.com/projects/polygons-the-flat-4-in-1-measuring-spoon-cool-design--3#/\" rel=\"nofollow\">链接</a>参与众筹，最低价为 14 美元。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161209220240UD5EL4Z76SHnqXls.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.502941\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161209220240fV6hxn8a9RDT5kbd.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.714706\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161209220240UkD8s1JG5RrALyIX.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666176\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161209220241QBHne7hMVgO4xuU3.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.100000\" data-format=\"png\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161209220241OPjHdKeVMfS0ClpI.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.563333\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Foodie Dice by Two Tumbleweeds</h3><p>菜谱虽好，有时也会让人感到厌倦。在美国中西部，就有一对喜欢在厨房里尝试新菜肴的姐妹，为了让每一次的实验都充满惊喜，她们设计了一套名为 <a href=\"http://www.foodiedice.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Foodie Dice</a> 的骰子。这些木质立方体的表面刻着不同的食材和调味料名称，需要你用扔的方式确定今天饭桌上的主角们。这是骰子的<a href=\"http://www.foodiedice.com/collections/seasonal-dinners\" rel=\"nofollow\">购买链接</a>，售价为 24 美元。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161209214309m7sGfrMbTA3c5LBa.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161209214309GxEN1OtzQdcKb5eL.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161209214309r5GYUeAPpMJg3FEn.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.110526\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161209214309N3qZHp8r1PueWwD2.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3><br></h3><p class=\"\"><br></p><p><br></p><h3>4 Cheese by Authentics</h3><p>芝士撒起来不太好把控？阿根廷设计师 Alejandro Ruiz 为德国家居品牌 <a href=\"https://www.authentics.de/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Autnentics</a> 设计的 <a href=\"https://www.authentics.de/en/products/cookingdinner/4cheese/\" rel=\"nofollow\">4 Cheese</a> 芝士研磨器可以让你更精准地对菜肴加以点缀。有别于传统的研磨器造型，它看起来像是一张卷起的纸，一大一小两个出口可以满足你对芝士位置的要求。这是它的<a href=\"https://www.shop.floetotto.de/Authentics/4CHEESE-Kaesereibe\" rel=\"nofollow\">购买链接</a>，售价为 10 欧元。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161209214147BKaxJdGM9jOnIEDr.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161209214146spxColvu5q4E6aZe.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201612092141468I5UPJ7XSt14faql.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161209214147c4dwzM9pV6jlYICP.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p>        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #323333} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} </style>  </p><h3>Frankfurter Brett Basic by Johannes Schreiter &amp; Joseph Schreiter</h3><p class=\"\">在去年成功推出了为大厨设计的模块化砧板 <a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/1461435280/frankfurter-brett-the-kitchen-workbench\" rel=\"nofollow\">Frankfurter Brett</a> 之后，来自德国的设计团队对其进行了一番针对普通用户的改造，推出了它的 Basic 版。通过在砧板周围加上支架和收纳盒，只要轻轻往旁边刮送，食材和垃圾就能完成归类，让以往混乱的场面变得干净不少。如果你对烹饪还不是很上手，在支架的帮助下，平板电脑或是菜谱也能触手可及。你可以通过<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/1461435280/frankfurter-brett-basic-100-grossartig\" rel=\"nofollow\">链接</a>参与众筹，最低价为 129 欧元。<br></p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161209215019Ecm2iqhXMsn8uGFO.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666176\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161209215019G9uFRdO3sMXHyt8g.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.860294\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161209215019zS8EpDU9ZhvT5PFG.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"2.129412\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>"}